\c 31
\s Ukufa kukaSawuli lamadodana akhe
\p
\v 1 AmaFilisti alwa-ke loIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 10.1-12.\x*; lamadoda akoIsrayeli abaleka phambi kwamaFilisti, awa efile entabeni yeGilibowa\x + 28.4. 2 Sam. 1.6,21. 21.12.\x*.
\v 2 AmaFilisti asenamathela kuSawuli lamadodana akhe; amaFilisti abulala uJonathani, loAbinadaba, loMaliki-Shuwa, amadodana kaSawuli\x + 14.49. 29.19.\x*.
\v 3 Lempi yaba nzima kuSawuli, abatshoki bamfica, amadoda edandili; wasesiba lobuhlungu kakhulu ngabatshoki\x + 2 Sam. 1.6.\x*.
\v 4 USawuli wasesithi kumthwali wezikhali zakhe: Hwatsha inkemba yakho, ungigwaze ngayo\x + Hlu. 9.54.\x*, hlezi laba abangasokanga bafike bangigwaze, badlale kubi ngami\x + Hlu. 14.3.\x*. Kodwa umthwali wezikhali zakhe kavumanga, ngoba wesaba kakhulu\x + 2 Sam. 1.14.\x*. Ngakho uSawuli wathatha inkemba, waziwisela phezu kwayo\x + 2 Sam. 1.10.\x*.
\v 5 Lapho umthwali wezikhali zakhe ebona ukuthi uSawuli usefile, laye waziwisela phezu kwenkemba yakhe, wafa kanye laye.
\v 6 Wafa-ke uSawuli lamadodana akhe amathathu lomthwali wezikhali zakhe labo bonke abantu bakhe ngalolosuku ndawonye\x + 1 Lan. 10.6.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Lapho amadoda akoIsrayeli ayengaphetsheya kwesigodi layengaphetsheya kweJordani ebona ukuthi amadoda akoIsrayeli abalekile, lokuthi uSawuli lamadodana akhe sebefile, atshiya imizi, abaleka; amaFilisti asefika, ahlala kiyo\x + 29.1,11. Josh. 17.16. Hlu. 6.33. Hos. 1.5.\x*.
\v 8 Kwasekusithi kusisa lapho amaFilisti efika ukuhlubula ababuleweyo, afica uSawuli lamadodana akhe amathathu bewile entabeni yeGilibowa.
\v 9 Asequma ikhanda lakhe, ahlubula izikhali zakhe\x + 17.51.\x*, athumela elizweni lamaFilisti inhlangothi zonke ukumemezela imibiko endlini yezithombe zabo lebantwini\x + 2 Sam. 1.20. Hlu. 16.23,24.\x*.
\v 10 Abeka izikhali zakhe\x + 21.9.\x* endlini kaAshitarothi\x + Hlu. 2.13.\x*. Abophela isidumbu sakhe\x + 2 Sam. 21.12. 1 Lan. 10.10.\x* emdulini weBeti-Shani\x + Josh. 17.11.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Kwathi abahlali beJabeshi-Gileyadi\x + 11.1-11. Hlu. 21.8.\x* sebezwile ngalokho amaFilisti akwenze kuSawuli,
\v 12 asukuma wonke amaqhawe, ahamba ubusuku bonke, athatha isidumbu sikaSawuli lezidumbu zamadodana akhe emdulini weBeti-Shani\x + 11.1-11. 2 Sam. 2.4-7.\x*, eza eJabeshi, azitshisa khona\x + 2 Lan. 16.14. 21.19. Jer. 34.5. Amos 6.10.\x*.
\v 13 Asethatha amathambo abo, awangcwaba\x + 2 Sam. 21.12,14.\x* ngaphansi kwesihlahla \w setamarisiki\w** eJabeshi\x + 22.6. 1 Lan. 10.12.\x*, azila ukudla\x + 7.6. 2 Sam. 12.16.\x* insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Gen. 50.10.\x*.